{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or a read only situation and a disabled component."}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"text":"Suggestions","type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true},{"text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeCompact"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"rol